  "3224940": {
    "name": "三九",
    "steam_appid": 3224940,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>《三九》是一款包含中式恐怖元素的第一人称悬疑解谜游戏。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras/66ed13594cfd5449bddd60c7d6a96257.avif?t=1733909268\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras_big/66ed13594cfd5449bddd60c7d6a96257.avif?t=1733909268 width=800 height=203 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras/49de8bc6c4cee9e42962995b1a286115.avif?t=1733909268\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras_big/49de8bc6c4cee9e42962995b1a286115.avif?t=1733909268 width=800 height=616 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras/c0002b312177b34fba9fb0d971bbefc3.avif?t=1733909268\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras_big/c0002b312177b34fba9fb0d971bbefc3.avif?t=1733909268 width=800 height=203 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>一、恐怖回忆，重启调查</strong>  <br> <br>1974 年的雪夜，一场意外让主角的童年蒙上阴影。亲眼目睹诡异的凶案现场，侥幸逃脱后却丧失记忆，只留下一道永久的伤疤。多年后，主角重回故土，决心亲自探寻案件的真凶。在这个充满神秘与希望的视角下，你将跟随主角一同揭开那段尘封的恐怖记忆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>二、神秘山村，暴雪来袭</strong> <br>古老的仪式、愚昧的宗教、落后的山村，处处弥漫着恐怖的气息。阴森的老宅、诡异的森林、神秘的洞穴，每一个场景都隐藏着未知的危险。中式恐怖元素的巧妙运用，让你在游戏中时刻感受到心跳加速的刺激。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>三、悬疑解谜，重重危机</strong>  <br>揭秘古老仪式的传统、解开宗教符号的谜题、找出隐藏在山村中的线索，解救更多的人，在解谜的过程中，逐渐接近真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>四、人性之辩，善恶交织</strong> <br>人性的善与恶交织在一起。你将在游戏中与他们相遇，他们的遭遇将影响着故事的发展。是谁在从中作恶？山神是否真实存在？真正的凶手身在何处？神秘祭祀到底为何？怎样救出更多的人？等着你来一探究竟。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras/eee3c4b9f7d4b7b22826e3205965d2e2.avif?t=1733909268\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras_big/eee3c4b9f7d4b7b22826e3205965d2e2.avif?t=1733909268 width=800 height=203 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>一、时代画卷，重温旧日时光</strong> <br>精美的 CG 插图，生动地展现出中国 70 年代到 80 年代的独特人文风貌。昏暗的小巷、古朴的建筑、充满年代感的服饰，每一处画面都仿佛带着你穿越时光，回到那个充满回忆的岁月。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras/000321e5bd169687f2f61d488359f0b9.avif?t=1733909268\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras_big/000321e5bd169687f2f61d488359f0b9.avif?t=1733909268 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras/3a0ad67f676d9bd5c641e954f9219258.avif?t=1733909268\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras_big/3a0ad67f676d9bd5c641e954f9219258.avif?t=1733909268 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras/25a7f76d3bbaaa46d670aeb62de814d2.avif?t=1733909268\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras_big/25a7f76d3bbaaa46d670aeb62de814d2.avif?t=1733909268 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>二、特色道具，勾起往昔回忆</strong> <br>众多具有时代特色的道具等你来使用和互动！神秘的信件、尘封的档案、老式绿屏电脑、破碎拼图…… 每一个道具都承载着那个时代的记忆，让你在游戏中重温往昔，感受这份三九的寒意。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras/289bb56c212f663a349a901502c4d244.avif?t=1733909268\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras_big/289bb56c212f663a349a901502c4d244.avif?t=1733909268 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras/43b9099d5ee4712960c8628fc4ceb9e0.avif?t=1733909268\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras_big/43b9099d5ee4712960c8628fc4ceb9e0.avif?t=1733909268 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras/aa9c073337429a41c5ed3a11e0321f21.avif?t=1733909268\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras_big/aa9c073337429a41c5ed3a11e0321f21.avif?t=1733909268 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras/cf13c47ac0bb52a20993e1ca046acb15.avif?t=1733909268\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras_big/cf13c47ac0bb52a20993e1ca046acb15.avif?t=1733909268 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras/cdcefe2d348270067b83339c5ce72d3c.avif?t=1733909268\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras_big/cdcefe2d348270067b83339c5ce72d3c.avif?t=1733909268 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>三、氛围渲染，沉浸鬼魅寒冬</strong> <br>游戏场景氛围渲染极具感染力，寒冷的冬季、诡异的乡村、破旧残败的工厂……每一个场景都似一幅浓墨重彩的油画，散发着浓浓的时代气息，让你仿佛置身于那个寒冷而黑暗的冬天。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras/64ec66e115721554505339db4ecd01e8.avif?t=1733909268\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras_big/64ec66e115721554505339db4ecd01e8.avif?t=1733909268 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras/7d83f1a78aae2f84e1a90c904c0f86c1.avif?t=1733909268\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras_big/7d83f1a78aae2f84e1a90c904c0f86c1.avif?t=1733909268 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras/8f4b2a9b52d1861b2f2d4ede1e0ffc0d.avif?t=1733909268\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras_big/8f4b2a9b52d1861b2f2d4ede1e0ffc0d.avif?t=1733909268 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>四、趣味解密，探索时代故事</strong> <br>多种小游戏互动解密玩法，融入历史元素。破解老照片秘密、解开旧信件谜题、找出老物件线索，探索时代故事，感受人性复杂与恐怖交织。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras/ecb9e5404b84d5ae51d94d14215fc158.avif?t=1733909268\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras_big/ecb9e5404b84d5ae51d94d14215fc158.avif?t=1733909268 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras/f95285251e02faf4c0f5f532e2fba42b.avif?t=1733909268\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras_big/f95285251e02faf4c0f5f532e2fba42b.avif?t=1733909268 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras/9b3b278739061a5c9212e2f2ae092241.avif?t=1733909268\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras_big/9b3b278739061a5c9212e2f2ae092241.avif?t=1733909268 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras/f34f1d972856385782162d3afa201d8e.avif?t=1733909268\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras_big/f34f1d972856385782162d3afa201d8e.avif?t=1733909268 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras/c18df8c3774b40c9bced5d147bc0b524.avif?t=1733909268\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras_big/c18df8c3774b40c9bced5d147bc0b524.avif?t=1733909268 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>快来倾听《三九》的故事，一同探索这个充满恐怖与悬疑的山村，寻找真凶，揭开人性的秘密。</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras/4c93ff36ac1a783e3c4cea9eb62a1371.avif?t=1733909268\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras_big/4c93ff36ac1a783e3c4cea9eb62a1371.avif?t=1733909268 width=800 height=203 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >三九是一款以手动益智、解谜推理、点击破解等众多元素集合的悬疑文字冒险游戏，玩家将扮演主角，以第一人称视觉在游戏众多场景中，寻找画面关键信息，点击收集解谜要素，完成互动小游戏，破解机关……最终推进案件推理，与剧情发展。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更多角色将在正式版中登场，敬请期待。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras/9e0318204b2afcc52935dd8422afe93d.avif?t=1733909268\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224940/extras_big/9e0318204b2afcc52935dd8422afe93d.avif?t=1733909268 width=800 height=258 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
